divs: Sighting Details Was outside smoking a cig at 8:00pm when I saw a star like object ascend until it disappeared. It was about the size of a bb held at arms length. It came from the west and kept going up and up and disintergrated into an orange ball. The orange ball also disappeared in less than a second. I see alot of planes because I live about 15 miles from the airport in Manitowoc WI. I don't believe this was a plane. I also wonder if this object landed somewhere in the west of my location.
Summary: Star like object ascends until it disappears
